reviewText: A funny weird horror film about a killer sex doll . 35 minutes of I can not believe someone pulled this off and did a great job of it !

If you're like me, you're tired of entertainment being watered down and censored as if we're all nine years old. The Sex Doll She-Bitch is a breath of fresh air. Raunchy, raw, and a hell of a lot of fun. Tuck Grandma into bed, grab a drink and enjoy yourself. Well worth the investment!
The junkie on the couch was the best acting I've ever seen! (I may be a little biased) Funny movie though. Watch it!
